{"tid":1901983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係8.31]被控阻礙警務人員執行職務罪　女子提堂後獲准保釋","createTime":"2020-02-28T06:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T06:27:43.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dca4d617538f31db221e216bad56b9945ae53866","tid":1901983,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"一名52歲家庭主婦去年8月底於旺角及太子的警民衝突中，被控一項阻礙警務人員執行職務罪，在屯門判裁法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官應辯方要求，將案件押後至4月22日再訊，以待辯方索閱控方文件。被告准以1000元擔保，期間不准離港，每星期須到警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n去年8月31日晚上，示威者在旺角及太子一帶與警方發生激烈衝突，多人被捕。被告當晚涉嫌於彌敦道與山東街交界，阻礙一名女警及一名男警員執行職務。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511436-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511436-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0WzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=bb845d4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511436-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b75042cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511436-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"deb89c2741c4aa895133d8cf12ef5ad3860d8465","tid":1901983,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"功能組別最後一個月，決勝關鍵係工程、建築測量、飲食、批發零售、進出口 (附懶人包)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/atdRoLV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/atdRoLV</a>"}]}